H4592">je</char> l'ai soufflée. <char style="w" strong="H4100">Pourquoi</char> ? <char style="w" strong="H5002">dit</char> l'Éternel <char style="w" strong="H3068">des</char> <char style="w" strong="H6635">armées</char>, <char style="w" strong="H3068">à</char> <char style="w" strong="H3282">cause</char> <char style="w" strong="H1004">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H7235">ma</char> <char style="w" strong="H1004">maison</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">qui</char> gît, tandis <char style="w" strong="H3282">que</char> chacun <char style="w" strong="H1004">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">vous</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">est</char> occupé <char style="w" strong="H1004">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">sa</char> propre <char style="w" strong="H1004">maison</char>. <verse eid="HAG 1:9" /><verse number="10" style="v" sid="HAG 1:10" />C'est <char style="w" strong="H3651">pourquoi</char>, à <char style="w" strong="H5921">cause</char> <char style="w" strong="H5921">de</char> vous, <char style="w" strong="H3607">les</char> <char style="w" strong="H8064">cieux</char> retiennent <char style="w" strong="H5921">la</char> <char style="w" strong="H2919">rosée</char>, <char style="w" strong="H8064">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H5921">la</char> terre retient <char style="w" strong="H5921">ses</char> <char style="w" strong="H2981">fruits</char>. <verse eid="HAG 1:10" /><verse number="11" style="v" sid="HAG 1:11" />J'ai <char style="w" strong="H7121">appelé</char> <char style="w" strong="H7121">la</char> <char style="w" strong="H2721">sécheresse</char> <char style="w" strong="H5921">sur</char> <char style="w" strong="H7121">la</char> terre, <char style="w" strong="H5921">sur</char> <char style="w" strong="H7121">les</char> <char style="w" strong="H2022">montagnes</char>, <char style="w" strong="H5921">sur</char> <char style="w" strong="H7121">le</char> <char style="w" strong="H1715">blé</char>, <char style="w" strong="H5921">sur</char> <char style="